# ── Trailer build artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Everything here is REGENERABLE from the scripts in this folder
# (scene.html + scene-server.mjs -> frames, then build-cine.ps1 -> video).
# We keep the small source + the final render in git; the heavy stuff is ignored.

# Rendered frame sequences (thousands of images, tens/hundreds of MB)
frames/
frames_cine/

# Encoded intermediate clips and muxed audio (rebuilt by ffmpeg)
clips/
*.m4a
concat.txt

# Copied system fonts (used only by the legacy gameplay build.ps1; they live in
# C:\Windows\Fonts — not ours to commit)
*.ttf

# Superseded large renders — keep only adversary-cinematic.mp4 (the final cut)
adversary-trailer.mp4
adversary-trailer-720share.mp4

# NOT ignored (kept in git on purpose):
#   scene.html, scene-server.mjs, build*.ps1, gen-*.mjs, list-voices.mjs,
#   subs.ass, audio/ (small VO/music/SFX mp3s — avoids paid re-generation),
#   adversary-cinematic.mp4 (the deliverable)
